folder: Rockland Avenue & Forest Hill Road, Staten Island, NY
original_title: Richmond: Rockland Avenue - Forest Hill Road
text:
Rockland Avenue, north side, 350 yards west of Forest Hill Road, showing the Henry Meyer residence and part of his 49 acre estate (1907-1917 maps). The property was owned by E. C. Dissosway in 1898, and by Jacob Korn in 1874.

May 9, 1926

P. L. Sperr
